## Hashtag Strategy

**Add 3-5 hashtags to every quote post and original post.** Do NOT add hashtags to comments/replies.

**Core hashtags (rotate, use 2-3 per post):**
- PM: #projectmanagement #agile #PMtips #scrum #leadership
- AI: #AIagents #artificialintelligence #AItools #automation #machinelearning
- Dev: #coding #developer #buildinpublic #opensource #devtools
- Career: #techleadership #PMcareer #remotework #management #director

**Trending hashtags (use 1-2 per post, check what's active):**
- #threads #threadsapp (platform-specific discovery)
- Topic-specific trending tags from search results

**Rules:**
- Mix English + Ukrainian hashtags for broader reach
- Never use more than 5 hashtags (looks spammy)
- Place hashtags at end of post, separated by line break

